Name: Hotham
Description:
The Division of Hotham consists of:

  • part of the Glen Eira City Council,
  • part of the Greater Dandenong City Council,
  • part of the Kingston City Council, and
  • part of the Monash City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Retail, health care, food services and education.
NameDerivation: Named after Sir Charles Hotham RN KCB, 1806-55. Hotham was Lieutenant-Governor of Victoria (1854-55) and the first Governor of Victoria (1855).
Members:
• O'Neil, C (ALP) 2013-
  • Crean, S (ALP) 1990-2013
  • Kent, L (ALP) 1980-1990
  • Johnston, J R (LP) 1977-1980
  • Chipp, D (LP/IND/DEM) 1969-1977
DemographicRating: Inner Metropolitan - situated in capital cities and consisting of well-established built-up suburbs.
